<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ACLEDA Mobile iOS - Setup Guide</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --card: #111827;
      --card-light: #1e293b;
      --text: #f8fafc;
      --subtext: #94a3b8;
      --primary: #3b82f6;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --success: #22c55e;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #020617 0%, #0f172a 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 50px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 52px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: var(--subtext);
      font-size: 18px;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 24px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.4);
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .card p {
      color: var(--subtext);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(59,130,246,0.15);
      color: #60a5fa;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    pre {
      background: #020617;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    code {
      color: #38bdf8;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: Menlo, monospace;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--subtext);
    }

    .step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--primary);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 80px;
      padding: 30px 0;
      color: var(--subtext);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .highlight {
      color: var(--success);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero {
        padding-top: 50px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
      }

      .hero p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      .container {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>ACLEDA Mobile iOS</h1>
      <p>
        Professional iOS project setup guide with Git workflow,
        CocoaPods installation, branch strategy, and Merge Request flow.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="grid">

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Git Setup</span>
        <h2>Global Git Configuration</h2>

        <p>Configure Git before cloning project.</p>

        <pre><code>git config --global user.name "Your Name"

git config --global user.email "your_email@example.com"

git config --global --list</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Clone Project</span>
        <h2>Clone Repository</h2>

        <pre><code>cd Desktop

git clone http://{localserverip}/kimseak/acleda-mobile-ios.git

cd acleda-mobile-ios</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">CocoaPods</span>
        <h2>Install Dependencies</h2>

        <pre><code>pod install</code></pre>

        <p>If CocoaPods is missing:</p>

        <pre><code>sudo gem install cocoapods</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Xcode</span>
        <h2>Open Workspace</h2>

        <pre><code>open YourProject.xcworkspace</code></pre>

        <p>
          <span class="highlight">Important:</span>
          Always open <code>.xcworkspace</code>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Git Flow</span>
        <h2>Create Branch</h2>

        <pre><code>git checkout develop
git pull origin develop

git checkout -b feature/home-ui</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Commit</span>
        <h2>Commit Changes</h2>

        <pre><code>git add .

git commit -m "feat: improve login validation"</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Push</span>
        <h2>Push Code</h2>

        <pre><code>git push -u origin feature/home-ui</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Merge Request</span>
        <h2>Create MR</h2>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div>Open GitLab</div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div>Go to Merge Requests</div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div>Create New Merge Request</div>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div>Select source and target branch</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Best Practice</span>
        <h2>Development Rules</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>Never commit directly to main branch</li>
          <li>Always use feature branches</li>
          <li>Pull latest develop before coding</li>
          <li>Review changed files before push</li>
          <li>Use clean commit messages</li>
          <li>Create Merge Request for every update</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <span class="badge">Troubleshooting</span>
        <h2>Useful Commands</h2>

        <pre><code>git status
git branch
git log --oneline
git pull
git push</code></pre>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>ACLEDA Mobile iOS Team • Senior Level Project Setup Guide</p>
    </div>

  </div>

</body>
</html>
